Description

Nydel Paris Coated Tablecloth EQUATEUR 62″ Round

Good news for your kitchen & terrace! No care! Just wipe with a sponge! Machine washable too!

Heavyweight – not flimsy – a real tablecloth (400 g/m²)!!

100% cotton with three layers of waterproof protective film & a stain-resistant finish.

Size: 62″ (5 ft. 2 in.) [160cm].

Made in France.
